程序包 MyException

  • 异常错误概要 
    异常错误 说明
    AtomElectronNumException
    This exception is about electron number in atom structure.
    AtomElementException
    This exception is about nucleus element in atom structure.
    AtomTrackNumException
    This exception is about track number in atom structure.
    DataNonScientificNumberException
    Deal with some exception when a more than 10000 number doesn't use scientific notation.
    DataScientificNumberException
    This exception is about illegal scientifc number notation.
    DataSyntaxException
    This exception is about data in file may doesn't fit syntax in specification.
    DegreeOutOfRangeException
    Planet's degree is out of range [0,360).
    FriendConflictException
    There are at least two friends with same names in data file.
    IllegalIntimacyInSocialTieException
    This exception may happens only in social network circle.
    IntermediaryNotExistException
    When calculate information diffusivity in social network circle, the intermediary that user inputs may not exist.
    MementoRollBackTooManyStepsException
    When roll back transition version, the number of versions rolled back may be greater than the total of versions.
    NonexistentFriendInSocialTieException  
    NoObjectOnTrackException  
    PlanetConflictException  
    SocialTieConflictException
